In d = 1 the model is exactly solvable in several impor-

tant cases. In the following we discuss the anisotropic

quantum XY model ͑⌬ = 0 and 0 ഛ ␥ ഛ 1͒ and the XXZ

model ͑␥ = 0͒. Also the XYZ model in zero ﬁeld, ␥

